'''Lezzayer''' d tamdint tamanaɣt n tegduda n Lezzayer, d tamdint i muqqren g temurt, sawalen-as daɣen imezdaɣ-ines Zzayer tamellalt neɣ El-Bahdja. Tezgad g yiri n [[Ilel Agrakal|yilel agrakal]], tamanaɣt n Zzayer tefka isem-is i yal agezday (tawilayt) n Zzayer. Tella gar timiṭropolin timuqranin g umenẓaw n [[Tafriqt|Tafrikt]] s 2 030 000 imezdaɣ g aseggas n [[2002]], yetwaḥsab azal n 2.947.446 imezdaɣ g useggas n [[2008]].
G tamdint n Zzayer kan adnaf azal n 4 250 000 imezdaɣ neɣ azal n 12% n ugdud azzayri. G yal tamurt
tesɛa agezday n Zzayer tillas akk d ugezday n [[Blida]], s unẓul [[Tipaza]], s utaram, [[Bumerdas]] s umalu.

== Aẓar n isem n Zzayer ==
Isem n Alger (Aljé) d issem aɛewwaj arumi n yisem "Alguère" s [[takatalant]] ; aneggaru-agi yeffeɣ-d g [[teɛrabt]] "ğazayer", Jazayer isem-is yefka [[Buluɣin mmis n Ziri]], win id ixelqen [[tadinastit tazirit]] ass-nni mi yesekka tamdint n Zzayer deg useggas n [[960]] f ugaluz n temdint taqdimt i yesɛan isem s terumant [[Icosium]], yefkayas issem n Zzayer At [[Mezɣenna]], caḍen izegzziyen i yefkan anamek n isem-agi i yetwafken sɣur Buluɣin Mis n Ziri. 

Azzegzi amezwaru yennad akken isem n Zzayer yetwakkes g tigzirin i yellan zdat usagen n temdint n Zzayer s teɛrabt (al-Jaza’ir) الجزائر, s [[teqbaylit]], tigzirin n at mezɣenna, Neɣ awal n “tagzirt” yezmer (akken i ɣilen arakalen [[inselmen]] n tallit talemmast) ad yini igger i yellan ger illel d [[Ṣeḥra]] igger i yezmer a tilli gyes tameddurt, “tajtagzirt n tmeddurt”. Azzegzi angaru yenna-d belli issem ad yillin fkan-t feljal tajmilt n baba-s n Buluɣin, [[Ziri mmis n Mennad]] , ihi, issem n Zzayer ad yilli yusa-d g Dziri, s tmaziɣt, Tiziri(anamek (lmaɛna)-ines tafat n uyyur/uggur), Mezɣenna yezmer daɣen ad tili talɣa tetwaɛerreb n Imezɣen ayen aɣ-d-yefk : “Tiziri n at Imezɣan”. Imuzdaɣ n Zzayer tamanaɣt qqaren Adziri/Tadzirit (dziri/dziriya) fakken ad ssiwlen i imuzdaɣ n tamanaɣt.

